{"type": "article", "id": 50634, "title": "这盏手工打磨的吊灯，灵感源自中国传统的雨帽｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-02-27T23:19:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 34901, "name": "Elliot Bastianon"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}, {"id": 48061, "name": "致家家居"}, {"id": 48062, "name": "Offecct"}, {"id": 48063, "name": "Morrama"}, {"id": 48064, "name": "朱妍澔"}, {"id": 48065, "name": "Lucy Kurrein"}, {"id": 48066, "name": "Martin Jakobsen"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 171, "image": "img/article/article_show/201802272213314hjXEmBpiCSyVdzg.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>CuCu &amp; Duplex by Martin Jakobsen </h3><p>捷克设计师 Martin Jakobsen 为调酒师设计了一系列玻璃器皿，其中包括一个形状像南瓜的玻璃杯和一个专为品鉴鸡尾酒而设计的容器。</p><p>名为 CuCu 的水杯受到蔬菜园中西葫芦形状的启发，吸管插入其中，顶部有一个上扬的角度。设计师将 CuCu 描述为“玻璃技术实验”，试图寻找新的食物造型方法。每个杯子都是手工制作且独一无二的。</p><p>Duplex 则像是一组圆形实验室烧瓶，一大一小嵌套在一起，可以用于盛放干冰。每个杯子都有自己的开口，一个用于啜饮液体，另一个用于释放烟雾。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227221414Pm8cHlVZSCbwdo9G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227221420kgjSUFHxubCAvZaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227221421FKtnuY8Sicxr7Nw6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562183\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227221426Ej1xhknG4dNDiOHf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/02/25/martin-jakobsen-elaborate-glassware-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Angle razor by Morram</h3><p>伦敦工业设计机构 Morrama 开发了一种针对千禧一代的铝制剃须刀，希望能够减少一次性用品所产生的废弃塑料。根据 Morrama 的说法，Angle 剃须刀使用可回收的一次性刀片，旨在提供一次性剃须刀的可替代产品。</p><p>Angle 剃须刀设计极简，有一个加重手柄，可在拇指和食指上创建平衡枢轴点，便于控制。手柄的样式旨在使用户尽可能近的拿着剃刀刀片进行精确修剪。此外，设计师还发现，使用单个刀片已被证明可减少皮肤刺激，而多个刀片可能会损伤皮肤表面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222319DosGOSIYexUCnZVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227221507mLVbD1i0Ix5a8Cqk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227221515lzXtBJn3EqvUxHjD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802272215359pdDsryaKJOeh0vM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227221552FQf0eJg2Ga93r6sD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227221712pSAs0GnkLt7HvMcf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.morrama.com/angle-razor\" rel=\"nofollow\">Morrama</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Lucy Sofa by Lucy Kurrein</h3><p>这款模块化沙发由英国设计师 Lucy Kurrein 为瑞典家具品牌 Offecct 设计，不仅有便于用笔记本电脑工作的可移动桌面，又有可以挂置衣物的衣架。</p><p>这款沙发名为 Lucy，考虑到酒店大堂、共享办公空间等现代化的工作环境，尤其是那些需要同时满足工作和社交互动的空间。沙发由安装在黑色钢框架上的独立软垫座椅组成，可连接在一起为公共空间创建定制座椅系统。挂衣架和旋转边桌可以散布在座位之间，而 USB 端口则隐藏在靠背下。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222332J13UWlPy2MDN76pj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802272223333dzt0f8GesCvuMar.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.810068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222333sH5wceO83TZoXDCI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667090\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802272223335iKnoIrLXgaxGO7V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222333B8TfbjAYFaORZPpr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.324027\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.offecct.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Offecct</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Kasa Lamp by Yen-Hao, Chu</h3><p>2017 年，台湾产品设计师朱妍澔在瑞士洛桑艺术设计大学拿到硕士学位后，加入家具品牌致家家居担任设计师。这款名为 Kasa 的吊灯是其设计的第一款产品，也是该品牌首次涉足照明领域的第一个作品。</p><p>吊灯的灵感源自中国传统的雨帽，可遮阳挡雨。厚实实木上极致细腻的雕刻，手工打磨光滑，木头最薄处仅 4 毫米，镂空的金属网悬空于上灯罩，形成悬浮的美感且防止组装时的磕碰，灯头电镀优雅的雾光黄铜，经典的拉丝工艺都精心打磨。售价 680 元起，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-c-s.w4002-14926849207.20.5652161bHAbh99&amp;id=562555814807\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222445bDFwP5v31sSVztHm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222445YGucfC1wsPZ6eBbr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222446yRb9TetPDUzvdJXM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.466000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222446H5COJpyLb4tlTNSP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222445307S8GgBPMbejWwa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.547656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222445ESAe4iQZuqp7Ildb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.633000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222446aDAtXy72FJwbvx5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.441000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Track Basket by Simon Legald for Normann Copenhagen</h3><p>在为丹麦设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 设计这一工业风收纳系列时，设计师 Simon Legald 在超市购物车的线性金属结构中找到了灵感。收纳筐对立两端的线对角线线条设计为相反的方向，造成视觉上交叉重叠的美感。</p><p>粉末涂层钢制篮子提供多种尺寸和灰色、铁锈色和白色三种颜色，可用于存放书籍、杂志、办公用品、玩具等其他物品。售价 45 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/track-basket-25x25xh9?v=356945\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018022722260109OZladTSombicGA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.486719\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222601ZvLpR85xuXirs7b4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.649219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222601al8zdWEeNUR32Xc0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.871094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222601PndfSlOrM01WwCay.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222601J3h2mlKXcYPyMTWG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.442187\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Straight Lines by Elliot Bastianon</h3><p>堪培拉家具设计师 Elliot Bastianon 最近发布了一个名为 Straight Lines 的新系列，这些作品由木头制成的直线结构组成，柔软的座垫部分与横平竖直的木制网格框架的坚实感形成鲜明对比。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>这一系列包括沙发、椅子、咖啡桌和长凳，所有产品都有类似的网格形式，有些框架保持着原木色调，有些则被涂成了蓝色、绿色等各种偏于俏皮、大胆的色彩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222631ikBEa0xmTZF7lgvs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711719\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802272226310siL9YlNBU4FzRx2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222631dW7Y1iIXlGeaEjJO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222631zdHwCZ7jY2vquQbf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.028125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222631tlebYgHuAJxIaQKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.886719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802272226317vKiwH2flWZjhm81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.825781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227222631JPjFot7XIY6NxaKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/straight-lines-is-a-collection-of-gridded-furniture-by-elliot-bastianon/straight-lines-elliot-bastianon-15/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}